Experiments:

Part 1: from Katie & Jen
- Toe spacers [USA - https://www.ptbodyfix.com/product-page/toe-spacers]
- Beam challenges
- Toe Yoga
- Rolling out plantar fascia and MTP joints
- Walking barefoot
- Research and purchase natural footwear, if relevant for you

https://tfc-shop.com/products/foot-and-ankle-tool-kit
https://www.ptbodyfix.com/product-page/Foot-Health-Kit

Part 2: from Ruth & Nick
- Footwear audit (FFFF), natural footwear daily drivers
- Foot mobility (explore texture/angles when barefoot)
- Toe splay (fingers, spreaders)
- Barefoot walk
- Barefoot run
- Barefoot hike
- Hacky drills from James: [watch at 3:50 minute of this video] https://youtu.be/aVZwV7OMkVo 

